- manage installation sources
- Manage different architectures
- Manage different installation protocls
- SLP support
- Create server configuration for 
    * HTTP Install Server
    * NFS Install Server
    * FTP Install Server
- Manage Multiple Sources

Workflow:

- Copy files from Media
    * Keep Source structure AS IS
    * After Copying parts of the source (CDs) are ro if possible
    * All Changes happen using symlinks and copies.
    * Support loop mounts of sources instead of copying them to system
- Make Source accessible via network.
- Announce Source via SLP
- Source View (Package Manager Feature)
- Manage Custom Sources
    * Custom, non suse packages
    * create package databases
    * product names, versions etc.

